Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.00,1:16:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and you went and took them off the\Nfloor. That's your problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.04,1:16:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me one more slide and we'll take a\Nbreak.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.71,1:16:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh\Nyeah, we calibrated the higher levels of
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.08,1:16:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness. You see enlightenment,\Netc. Now, what was the purpose of this?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.32,1:16:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The purpose of this was because it's\Nthere's never been
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.12,1:16:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,like proof of spiritual realities.\NThere's never been demonstration,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.32,1:16:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,convincing demonstration,\Nverifiable proof, verifiable evidence of
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.88,1:16:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the states of higher consciousness.\NWe take people's word for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.19,1:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The church says somebody's a saint, etc.\NBut there's never been any actual
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.04,1:16:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,objective verification of levels of\Nconsciousness or spiritual states,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.15,1:17:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so-called spiritual realities. So the\Npurpose of this was to document and of
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.52,1:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,course we've done this with whole groups\Nin previous years.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.96,1:17:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We've doc documented the existence of\Nthis reality
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.52,1:17:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and we see that it's on that whole curve\Nof consciousness that it goes all the
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.08,1:17:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,way up to infinite all the way up to\Ninfinite.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.80,1:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,With kinesiology we've got that the in\Nthe power of the field which is
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.52,1:17:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,continuously present is infinite\Ninfinite. infinite.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.56,1:17:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We got that there are calibrated levels\Nof consciousness classically termed
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.04,1:17:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightened from 600 and up. Although\Nrare, they are always the same
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.92,1:17:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout history and we can calibrate\Nthe level of consciousness of any of the
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.64,1:17:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,great saints or great spiritual teachers\Nof all time. Therefore, they are not
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.19,1:18:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,figments of people's imagination\Nor wishful thinking or are they unreal.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.48,1:18:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the person who says they're not\Nreal is the one who's being unreal
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.00,1:18:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're limited to mechanistic\Nreductionism, which doesn't even get up
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.64,1:18:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to 450. I think mechanistic reductionism\Nis about 420.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.36,1:18:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mechanistic reductionism is over 420,\N425.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.84,1:18:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,mechanistic reductionism. It isn't real\Nunless you can measure it way it
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.84,1:18:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates the 420. So it's sort of dumb\Nactually. I don't wish to be insulting
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.67,1:18:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is pretty dumb.\NAll these great levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.48,1:18:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,exist but beyond that person's\Nunderstanding. Next one then we're going
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.76,1:18:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to take a break.\NThe verification of spiritual reality
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.80,1:18:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then is one of the things we did. And\Nwhat we did this morning is we went
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.36,1:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,through form. We went through\Nrecognition, awareness, observer,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.15,1:18:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,witness. And we talked about the nature\Nof consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.60,1:19:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the purpose of all the\Nlectures is to reach this realization.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.67,1:19:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Okay. No, we we'll stop there.\Nliquid there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.84,1:19:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what we did this morning was try to\Nrecapitulate where we started so that
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.15,1:19:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we're all in the same all in the same\Nfield, right? We're all in the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.71,1:19:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Does everybody understand everything\Nsaid this morning? Anybody left?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.19,1:19:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have questions and answers later\Nbecause I want everybody to understand
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.28,1:19:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,what we've talked about.\NEverything comes into existence as a
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.60,1:19:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,result of the field. The totality of the\Nfield. That's the essential point that
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.64,1:20:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,jumps you 450 lifetimes.\NWe'll resume after a short break.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.64,1:20:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Those that are not here don't deserve to\Nhear what we're going to say anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.15,1:20:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we don't want to be tardy to\Nheaven, do we?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.32,1:20:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to clear an energy that came up\Nduring the lecture
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.67,1:20:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the archetype of the religionist\Nin me
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.64,1:20:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,because self-realization means that the\Nabsolute authority of the truth of the
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.67,1:20:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity of God as the essence of your\Nexistence comes from within.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.44,1:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that up brought up a fear of heresy in\Nthe archetype of mind religionist
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.44,1:21:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,because\Ntraditionally you're supposed to believe
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.08,1:21:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're told to believe and anything\Nelse is heresy. The pure heresy came up
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.64,1:21:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so I had to go outside and clear the\Nprayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.92,1:21:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If it came up in me that means it's in\Nthe unconscious of uh
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.40,1:21:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,probably everyone here. Yeah.\NYet we have permission to realize the
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.23,1:21:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,truth of our own existence.\NWe have the we have permission
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.40,1:21:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,collectively as a group. I have\Npermission to ask this question. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.32,1:21:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission collectively as a\Ngroup to realize the truth of the source
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.12,1:21:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of our own existence.\NResist.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.52,1:21:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission.\NI feel better.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.48,1:21:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It really came up as a bad energy and I\Nheard myself going flat. I thought, God,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.64,1:21:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there's somewhere energy in me here.\NYeah. Out of the unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.96,1:21:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Young's concepts of the archetypes is\Nquite interesting, you know. So, as you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.19,1:22:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,get to certain levels, you pull up the\Nkarma of all kinds of things, both
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.96,1:22:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,positive and negative. There you go.\NAll right. So, we calibrated the levels
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.56,1:22:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness. We showed how they\Nevolve through evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.88,1:22:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The profound impact it has on every\Naspect of human life. How one changes
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.71,1:22:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,one's karmic potential by making\Ndecisions every instant.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.36,1:22:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a couple lectures ago we showed the\Ndistribution of the levels of
