Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.80,1:23:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that, folks?\NAre you going to undo the karma of
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.52,1:23:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,having slaughtered innocent people by\Nthe millions?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.92,1:23:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In my lifetime, 100 million have been\Nslaughtered.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.56,1:23:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in this lifetime, one lifetime, 100\Nmillion. So, how do you undo that karma?
